=== sw-cor24-rpg-ii Minimal RPG-II Demo ===
Program:
H  control header
F  input file INFIL
I  field A0105  (10-char input slice)
C  MOVE A0105 -> calc work field
O  DETAIL output (10 chars)

Current boundary:
- Real today: build path, external tiny source-deck loading, fixed H/F/I/C/O
  source parsing, one extracted field, one MOVE-style calc stage, one
  output-line format stage, CLI demo surface.
- Placeholder today: source shape is still fixed; no general RPG parser, no
  variable C-spec execution, no general O-spec formatting, no arbitrary
  user-supplied RPG program execution yet.

Current expected output:
RECORD 01A
RECORD 02B
RECORD 03C

Authored source: rpg2.hlasm
Tiny demo source: tiny_rpg_demo.src
